name: Paper Garland Bunting Note Card
description:
For special occasions, the paper garland "faux bunting" note card features little paper pennants cut by hand and strung along white string over smooth, white card stock. 

Perfect for celebrating birthdays, graduations, weddings, new babies or anything else full of happiness, the card measures 5.5" x 4" when folded, is blank on the inside, and comes with a white envelope.

Available in four color combinations.

options.name: mustard yellow, gray, and cobalt blue
